## 📁 Projekt-Struktur

```
/[projekt-name]
├── README.md              # Auto-updated
├── PROJECT_PLAN.md        # Auto-updated
├── CHANGELOG.md          # Auto-generated
├── .windsurf/
│   └── rules/            # Diese Datei
├── src/
│   ├── [feature]/        # Feature-Module
